Filime yumwimerere yari hafi yabagore batatu basunika imyaka mirongo itatu bagerageza gushira amanga kugirango bahindure ubuzima bwabo, ariko ibyateganijwe byari bifite izindi gahunda kuri bo. Noneho murukurikirane, abadamu baragarutse, iki gihe basunika imyaka mirongo ine. Nubwo bakuze kandi bafite ubwenge, bamenye ko ubu bafite ibibazo byinshi harimo nubusabane bwabo butari bwiza. <ref name=":0" />

